### 请求 /cps/rebate-config/create 接口 => 成功（全局兜底配置）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/rebate-config/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "memberLevelId": null,
  "platformCode": null,
  "rebateRate": 80.0000,
  "maxRebateAmount": 0.00,
  "minRebateAmount": 0.00,
  "priority": 1,
  "status": 1
}

